"metaSummary_en": "Mega Altaria ex Espeon is still by far the most played deck (7.57% usage) but caps at 50.58% win rate; the best genuinely playable win rate belongs to Suicune ex Baxcalibur (52.08%), ahead of Mega Altaria ex Gourgeist (51.69%) and Mega Blaziken ex Greninja (51.37%). The meta is very stable, dominated by Mega decks and Magnezone/Miraidon variants, with no order changes in the top 10. High-win-rate outsiders to watch: Iron Valiant Iron Boulder (52.88%), Sylveon ex Mega Altaria ex (52.87%, boosted by the new set) and Mega Charizard Y ex Entei ex (52.30%). Hot news: the Everyday Wonders mini-expansion launches today (Monday June 29, 6:00 p.m. PDT; June 30 in Asia), led by Mega Diancie ex alongside Pikachu, Piplup, Snorlax, Greedent and Sylveon. July follows with the Everyday Wonders Emblem Event, Community Week and the Hisuian Zorua Drop Event, then the major Ruler of the Skies expansion (~July 30, Mega Rayquaza ex).",
